rows.name:
Me and Harghal, we both
have a flair for dancing.

rows.label: tlk45450111_03_msg0002
rows.name:
That's why Bahn-sama took such a
shine to us, and now we're his
personal dancing girls and secretaries.

rows.label: tlk45450111_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Though if I'm honest, I think he
likes Harghal more than he likes me.

rows.label: tlk45450111_03_msg0004
tlk45450111_03_msg0005
rows.name:
I almost wish life could
go on like this forever.
